      <div class="msgContentFrame">I am level 17 gladiator and still don't have body armour. Seems like the game wants me to level weaver and leatherworker aswell. I am arm 15, smith 12 and goldsmith 10. The lack of an auction house makes it near impossible for me to get the required materials for body armour and even legs etc. I cannot use the Market Wards. They are completely useless and NPCs don't sell the required non-arm/smth/gs mats I need. Anyone else encountering these difficulties? </div>
